. Web3 Subscription NFT L1
Overview

Web3 Subscription NFT L1 enables subscription-based access using NFTs as programmable access tokens.

Features
NFT-based subscriptions
Time-based access control
Transferable subscription rights
Automated renewals
Programmable access logic
Architecture
NFT Registry

Stores subscription tokens and metadata.

Access Control Layer

Validates subscription status.

Renewal Engine

Handles recurring subscription logic.

Integration APIs

Connects with platforms and services.

Use Cases
Membership platforms
Content subscriptions
SaaS access control
Community memberships
